{"tid":966482,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：收到金正恩的信件　期待盡快再次會面","createTime":"2019-01-02T23:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T00:41:05.000Z","uid":66271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"60b263486435667e9d091900f48abc271cb33f76","tid":966482,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T23:31:45.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）周三（2日）表示，收到一封朝鮮領袖金正恩的信件，並預計雙方快將再次會面。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在白宮向傳媒提及此事，指自己和金正恩建立一段良好的關係，他又提到與朝鮮的談判時，並沒有強調對方棄核的速度。<br />\n金正恩在周二（1月1日）發表元旦講話。他表示不會再製造、試驗和使用或擴散核武器，並促請美國就無核化進程採取相應措施。金正恩強調，如美國堅持向朝鮮提出單方面要求，平壤政府將無可避免地尋找新出路。"},{"pid":"cbab00817ae40656685c58ba17533c539af518c3","tid":966482,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T23:32:15.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"5a14e357c50c7d024ca61b36b64810daecda3064","tid":966482,"uid":53773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T23:32:52.000Z","msg":"北韓寄去美國幾耐到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47df2bb574127d7f415c20bb4fad6b61396495b","tid":966482,"uid":810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T23:34:16.000Z","msg":"好朋友"},{"pid":"35f64ba8e8d834d2d5b5a2c417ed21d22481c2e8","tid":966482,"uid":23058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T23:37:16.000Z","msg":"T先生: 可否阻你十八秒鐘看看信"},{"pid":"4a3137be4cb4b0db5970a6e65fd25e957c6bade2","tid":966482,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35f64ba8e8d834d2d5b5a2c417ed21d22481c2e8","tid":966482,"uid":23058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T23:37:16.000Z","msg":"T先生: 可否阻你十八秒鐘看看信"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T23:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚無面呀金仔"},{"pid":"88a8b64539ce3668ad2c40bb68849cf8bb35853f","tid":966482,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T23:59:11.000Z","msg":"金仔醒呀<br />\n<br />\n北泡建立平價生產線幫美帝打工<